OL,3,CFamily of boy, 12, killed in hit-and-
OL,4,Crun urge suspect to 'do the right
OL,5,Cthing'
OL,7,FA family has made a fresh plea for a
OL,8,Fhit-and-run suspect to "do the right
OL,9,Fthing" as they continue to wait for
OL,10,Fjustice.
OL,12,FMore than two years have passed since
OL,13,F12-year-old Keaton Slater was killed
OL,14,Fin Radford, Coventry.
OL,16,FKeaton was hit by a 'speeding' BMW on
OL,17,FRadford Road on June 14, 2024. Police
OL,18,Fsaid the driver was believed to have
OL,19,Fbeen travelling at around 80mph on the
OL,20,F30mph road.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
