CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782134325
OL,3,CFamily of boy, 12, killed in hit-and-
OL,4,Crun urge suspect to 'do the right
OL,5,Cthing'
OL,7,FParents Clint and Louise Slater said
OL,8,Fthey are still seeking answers more
OL,9,Fthan two years after losing Keaton.
OL,11,FSuspect Dolars Aleksanders remains in
OL,12,FLatvia and hasn't been extradited to
OL,13,Fthe UK for legal proceedings.
OL,15,FKeaton's death rocked the community,
OL,16,Fwith hundreds of people attending a
OL,17,Fmemorial in Coventry to remeber him a
OL,18,Fweek after he died.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782134325
OL,3,CFamily of boy, 12, killed in hit-and-
OL,4,Crun urge suspect to 'do the right
OL,5,Cthing'
OL,7,FClint issued a direct appeal to
OL,8,FAleksanders, saying: "Do the right
OL,9,Fthing."
OL,11,FLouise added: "Keaton was just walking
OL,12,Fhome that day, doing nothing wrong. We
OL,13,Fjust want answers and we are not
OL,14,Fgetting them."
OL,16,FLouise said she knows Keaton would
OL,17,Fhave plenty to say about the wait for
OL,18,Fjustice, adding: "He would be going
OL,19,Fballistic!
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782134325
OL,3,CFamily of boy, 12, killed in hit-and-
OL,4,Crun urge suspect to 'do the right
OL,5,Cthing'
OL,7,F"He would be sitting on the sofa
OL,8,Fsaying, 'Have you caught him yet?' and
OL,9,Fthe guilt there is killing me."
OL,11,FBrother Josh added: "Two years on and
OL,12,Fstill does not feel real. We will
OL,13,Fnever give up until we get that
OL,14,Fjustice.
OL,16,F"You touched the hearts of thousands
OL,17,Fand thousands of people, Keats. We
OL,18,Fwill always keep your memory alive.
OL,26,@qD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
