OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782134325
OL,3,CFamily of boy, 12, killed in hit-and-
OL,4,Crun urge suspect to 'do the right
OL,5,Cthing'
OL,7,F"I wish you had the chance to grow up
OL,8,Fand had the chance to live your life.
OL,9,FIt just breaks my heart."
OL,11,FA spokesman for West Midlands Police
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with the
OL,13,Ffamily and friends of Keaton.
OL,15,F"Our investigation into the collision
OL,16,Fand the driver is very much active,
OL,17,Fand we are grateful for all the
OL,18,Fsupport and patience we have received
OL,19,Fso far in the pursuit of justice for
OL,20,FKeaton.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
