OL,3,CFamily of boy, 12, killed in hit-and-
OL,4,Crun urge suspect to 'do the right
OL,5,Cthing'
OL,7,F"Our determination to achieve this is
OL,8,Fas strong as ever, and we continue to
OL,9,Fwork closely with the Crown
OL,10,FProsecution Service (CPS)."
